---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const pageTitle = 'Terms & Conditions';
---
<BaseLayout title={pageTitle}>
  <div class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white shadow-sm rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-10">Last updated: February 21, 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">

          <p>This document is an electronic record in terms of the Information Technology Act, 2000 and the rules thereunder, as applicable. This document is published in accordance with the provisions of Rule 3(1) of the Information Technology (Intermediaries Guidelines) Rules, 2011, which require publishing the rules, regulations, privacy policy, and Terms of Use for access or usage of the website https://www.techlogicvibe.com/ (hereinafter referred to as the "Platform").</p>

          <p>The Platform is owned and operated by <strong class="text-slate-800">SABI TECH</strong>, with its registered office at Rose Avenue, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India (hereinafter referred to as 'SABI TECH', 'we', 'us', 'our'). SABI TECH operates under the brand name <strong class="text-slate-800">Tech Logic Vibe</strong> and provides professional software development services, technical consultation, and digital solutions.</p>

          <p class="font-semibold text-slate-700 bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500">BY ACCESSING, BROWSING, OR USING THIS PLATFORM, OR BY ENGAGING SABI TECH FOR ANY SERVICE, YOU AGREE TO BE BOUND BY THESE TERMS AND CONDITIONS. PLEASE READ THEM CAREFULLY BEFORE PROCEEDING.</p>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4">1. Nature of Services</h2>
            <p class="mb-3">SABI TECH provides the following professional services:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-2">
              <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Consultation &amp; Advisory:</strong> Paid discovery sessions, requirement workshops, technical advisory meetings, and solution scoping calls.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Software Development:</strong> Custom mobile applications (Android &amp; iOS), web applications, e-commerce platforms, multi-vendor marketplaces, and AI/ML solutions.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Maintenance &amp; Support:</strong> Post-delivery bug fixes, enhancements, performance monitoring, and ongoing technical support.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Digital Solutions:</strong> UI/UX design, system integration, API development, and cloud deployment services.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4">2. Fees &amp; Payment Terms</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-3">
              <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Consultation Fees:</strong> SABI TECH charges a fee for all consultation and advisory meetings. The fee for each session will be communicated and agreed upon prior to the meeting. Payment must be completed before the session is confirmed and scheduled.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Project Fees:</strong> Software development projects are priced based on scope, complexity, and timeline. A detailed proposal and quote will be shared before work commences. Projects are typically billed on a milestone or advance-payment basis as agreed in the project agreement.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Payment Methods:</strong> Payments may be made via UPI, bank transfer, credit/debit card, or any other method agreed upon. All payments are processed securely.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Taxes:</strong> All applicable taxes (including GST) will be added to the fees as per prevailing Indian tax laws and will be reflected in the invoice.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-slate-700">Late Payments:</strong> Delayed payments may result in pausing of active development work until dues are cleared. SABI TECH reserves the right to charge interest on overdue payments at the rate of 1.5% per month.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4">3. Service Delivery</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-3">
              <li>All timelines and delivery schedules will be outlined in the project proposal or service agreement. SABI TECH will make every effort to meet the agreed timelines.</li>
              <li>Delays caused by client inaction, delayed feedback, change in requirements, or force majeure events shall not be the liability of SABI TECH.</li>
              <li>Software deliverables will be handed over digitally (via repository access, deployment links, or secure file transfer).</li>
              <li>Acceptance of a deliverable by the client constitutes confirmation that the milestone is complete and satisfactory.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-3">
              <li>Upon full payment of all agreed fees, the client will own the intellectual property rights to the custom software developed specifically for them under the project.</li>
              <li>SABI TECH retains ownership of all pre-existing code libraries, frameworks, tools, and methodologies used in the development process. A non-exclusive licence to use these in the delivered product is granted to the client.</li>
              <li>Any work product created during a consultation session remains the intellectual property of SABI TECH unless explicitly transferred in writing.</li>
              <li>The Platform design, content, brand name 'SABI TECH', and 'Tech Logic Vibe' are the exclusive intellectual property of SABI TECH and may not be reproduced without written permission.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4">5. Confidentiality</h2>
            <p>Both SABI TECH and the client agree to keep confidential all proprietary information, business data, technical specifications, and any other sensitive information shared during the course of service delivery. This obligation survives the termination of any project or engagement.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4">6. Client Obligations</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-3">
              <li>Clients must provide accurate, complete, and timely information, feedback, and approvals required for project progress.</li>
              <li>Clients are responsible for ensuring that any content, data, or materials they provide do not infringe third-party rights or violate applicable laws.</li>
              <li>Clients must not use any SABI TECH service for any unlawful, fraudulent, or harmful purpose.</li>
              <li>Clients agree to honour all payment obligations as per the agreed terms and invoices.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-3">
              <li>SABI TECH's liability to any client for any cause whatsoever shall be limited to the total fees paid by the client to SABI TECH for the specific service in question.</li>
              <li>SABI TECH shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages, including loss of revenue, loss of data, or business interruption.</li>
              <li>SABI TECH does not guarantee that any software will be completely free of bugs or errors but commits to resolving critical issues reported within the agreed warranty period.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4">8. Termination</h2>
            <p>Either party may terminate a service engagement with written notice. Upon termination, the client shall pay for all work completed up to the termination date. Refunds (if any) shall be governed by the Refund &amp; Cancellation Policy available on this Platform.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4">9. Governing Law &amp; Dispute Resolution</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-3">
              <li>These Terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India.</li>
              <li>Any disputes arising out of or in connection with these Terms shall first be attempted to be resolved amicably through mutual discussion.</li>
              <li>If unresolved, disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India.</li>
              <li>All communications relating to disputes must be sent in writing to <a href="mailto:info@techlogicvibe.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">info@techlogicvibe.com</a>.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4">10. Modifications to Terms</h2>
            <p>SABI TECH reserves the right to modify these Terms at any time. Updates will be published on this page with a revised date. Continued use of the Platform or services after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms.</p>
          </section>

          <section class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <p><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Company:</span> SABI TECH</p>
              <p><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Brand:</span> Tech Logic Vibe</p>
              <p><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Email:</span> <a href="mailto:info@techlogicvibe.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">info@techlogicvibe.com</a></p>
              <p><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Phone:</span> <a href="tel:+917200650707" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">+91 7200650707</a></p>
              <p><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Address:</span> Rose Avenue, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India</p>
              <p><span class="font-medium text-slate-700">Business Hours:</span> Monday – Friday, 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM IST</p>
            </div>
          </section>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
